-{\\alpha}. Our analysis will aid in the\ndefinition of future observatories that aim to link dynamics in the\nchromosphere and transition region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Aug 2017 18:38:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
