ion yields quite reliable predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Sep 2017 10:54:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Nov 2017 07:37:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 09:57:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
